  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium-high heat.",
    "2. Add the sliced beef and cook until browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "3. Add the onion and garlic and cook until softened, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "4. Stir in the spicy mix and cook for 1 minute.",
    "5. Add the tomato and cook until heated through, about 2 minutes.",
